#. Tag: title
#: splitter.docbook:8
#, no-c-format
msgid "<title>File Splitter</title>"
msgstr "<title>सञ्चिकाविभाजकः</title>"

#. Tag: primary
#: splitter.docbook:10
#, no-c-format
msgid "<primary>File Splitter</primary>"
msgstr "<primary>सञ्चिकाविभाजकः</primary>"

#. Tag: para
#: splitter.docbook:12
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This function splits one (large) file up into multiple smaller files so that "
"they can be placed on smaller media (&eg; ZIP drives, ...) or sent by email. "
"The multiple files can be combined again to recreate the original file. "
"&krusader; and <trademark class=\"copyright\">Total Commander</trademark> "
"split/combine functions are compatible. To split a file choose <menuchoice> "
"<guimenu>File</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Split</guimenuitem> </menuchoice> or "
"<keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl; <keycap>P</keycap></keycombo>: a "
"<guilabel>Split</guilabel> dialog will open to confirm the operation."
msgstr ""
"एतत् कार्यं एकां (बृहत्) सञ्चिकां बहुषु लघुसञ्चिकासु विभजति येन ताः लघुमाध्यमेषु (&eg; ZIP "
"ड्राइव्, ...) स्थापयितुं वा ईमेलद्वारा प्रेषयितुं वा शक्यन्ते । बहुसञ्चिकाः पुनः संयोजयित्वा "
"मूलसञ्चिकां पुनः निर्मातुं शक्यन्ते । &krusader; तथा <trademark class=\"copyright"
"\">कुलसेनापति</trademark> विभाजन/संयोजनकार्यं सङ्गतम् अस्ति । सञ्चिकां विभक्तुं "
"<menuchoice> <guimenu>सञ्चिका</guimenu> <guimenuitem>विभाजनम्</guimenuitem> </"
"menuchoice> अथवा <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl; <keycap>P</keycap></"
"keycombo>: क्रियायाः पुष्ट्यर्थं <guilabel>Split</guilabel> संवादः उद्घाट्यते ।"

#. Tag: para
#: splitter.docbook:26
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If the name of the original file is <filename>foo</filename>, then the name "
"of the smaller files will be <filename>foo.000 foo.001 foo.002</filename> "
"&etc; There is no theoretical limit in the number of smaller files, but it "
"is recommended to limit the number to a maximum of 1023 files. &krusader; "
"creates a <filename>foo.crc</filename> file. This file contains the name, "
"size and the crc checksum of the original file. It is possible to combine "
"the file without the <filename>foo.crc</filename> file but in this case "
"&krusader; cannot check if the original file was recreated correctly."
msgstr ""
"यदि मूलसञ्चिकायाः नाम <filename>foo</filename> अस्ति तर्हि लघुसञ्चिकानां नाम "
"<filename>foo.000 foo.001 foo.002</filename> &etc; लघुसञ्चिकानां संख्यायां "
"सैद्धान्तिकसीमा नास्ति, परन्तु अधिकतमं १०२३ सञ्चिकानां संख्यां सीमितं कर्तुं शस्यते । "
"&krusader; <filename>foo.crc</filename> सञ्चिकां निर्माति । अस्मिन् सञ्चिकायां "
"मूलसञ्चिकायाः नाम, आकारः, crc checksum च अस्ति । <filename>foo.crc</filename> "
"सञ्चिकां विना सञ्चिकां संयोजयितुं शक्यते किन्तु अस्मिन् सन्दर्भे &krusader; मूलसञ्चिका सम्यक् "
"पुनः निर्मितवती वा इति परीक्षितुं न शक्नोति ।"

#. Tag: para
#: splitter.docbook:39
#, no-c-format
msgid "An example of a <filename>foo.crc</filename> file:"
msgstr "<filename>foo.crc</filename> सञ्चिकायाः उदाहरणम् :"

#. Tag: programlisting
#: splitter.docbook:41
#, no-c-format
msgid "filename=foo size=432998467868 crc32=21EB719A"
msgstr "सञ्चिकानाम=foo आकार=432998467868 crc32=21EB719A"

#. Tag: para
#: splitter.docbook:42
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"To combine the multiple files choose, select a partial file <filename>foo."
"xxx</filename> and choose <menuchoice> <guimenu>File</guimenu> "
"<guimenuitem>Combine files...</guimenuitem> </menuchoice> or <keycombo "
"action=\"simul\">&Ctrl; <keycap>B</keycap></keycombo>. The target folder is "
"the inactive panel and can be changed. The file names must be numbered in "
"ascending order: <filename>foo.001, foo.002, foo.003</filename> &etc; or "
"have letters in ascending order: (\" <userinput> <command>split</command> "
"<option>-b</option> </userinput>letter method\") <filename>fileaa, fileab, "
"fileac</filename> &etc; If the file <filename>foo.crc</filename> is found in "
"the same folder as the partial files, &krusader; will use this file to check "
"the combined file for errors."
msgstr ""
"बहुसञ्चिकानां संयोजनाय चिनोतु, आंशिकसञ्चिकां चिनोतु<filename> फू.xxx</filename> तथा "
"चिनोतु<menuchoice><guimenu> संचिका</guimenu><guimenuitem> सञ्चिकाः संयोजयन्तु...</"
"guimenuitem></menuchoice> वा<keycombo action=\"simul\"> &amp;Ctrl;<keycap> "
"ख</keycap></keycombo> . लक्ष्यपुटं निष्क्रियपटलम् अस्ति, परिवर्तनं च कर्तुं शक्यते । "
"सञ्चिकानामानि आरोहणक्रमेण संख्याकृतानि भवेयुः:<filename> फू.००१, फू.००२, फू.००३</"
"filename> &amp;इत्यादि; आरोहणक्रमेण वा अक्षराणि भवन्ति: (&quot;"
"<userinput><command> भंज</command><option value=-b> -ख</option></userinput> "
"अक्षरविधिः&quot;) २.<filename> fileaa, fileab, fileac इति</filename> &amp;"
"इत्यादि; यदि सञ्चिका<filename> foo.crc</filename> आंशिकसञ्चिकानां समानपुटे दृश्यते, "
"&amp;krusader; संयुक्तसञ्चिकायाः दोषाणां जाँचार्थं एतां सञ्चिकां उपयुज्यते ।"
